{"id": 5219, "title": "Ticket #5219: Memory leak in ClassAd function split()", "description": "<blockquote>\nThe <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=ClassAd\" title=\"Class Ad\">ClassAd</a></span> function split() that's defined in the Condor utils lib allocates an <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=ExprList\" title=\"Expr List\">ExprList</a></span> for the result of the function, which is then leaked. This is similar to the leak in splitUserName() and splitSlotName(), which was fixed in <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=3082\" title=\"memory leak in classad functions returing lists\">#3082</a></span>. The same fix should be used here.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2015-Aug-20 11:54:53 by johnkn:</em> <br/>\n\nCODE_REVIEW: change looks good. -tj</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-Aug-27 12:43</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=45732\">[45732]</a></span>: copy edited versions of 8.2.10 version history items into the 8.3.8 version history: <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=5219\" title=\"Memory leak in ClassAd function split()\">#5219</a></span> <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=5234\" title=\"condor_vacate ignores other arguments when -constraint is passed.\">#5234</a></span> <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=5236\" title=\"Fix pslot preemption for user priority\">#5236</a></span> <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=5240\" title=\"collector crashes on RHEL7 when more than 1023 fds active\">#5240</a></span>  (By Karen Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-Aug-20 09:57</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=45641\">[45641]</a></span>: Docs for <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=ClassAd\" title=\"Class Ad\">ClassAd</a></span> function split() memory leak fix. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=5219\" title=\"Memory leak in ClassAd function split()\">#5219</a></span>  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-Aug-13 10:48</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=45601\">[45601]</a></span>: Fix memory leak in <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=ClassAd\" title=\"Class Ad\">ClassAd</a></span> function split(). <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=5219\" title=\"Memory leak in ClassAd function split()\">#5219</a></span> Since the split() function creates an <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=ExprList\" title=\"Expr List\">ExprList</a></span> for its result, the Value object needs to delete that <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=ExprList\" title=\"Expr List\">ExprList</a></span> when it goes out of scope.  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "defect", "last_change": "2015-Aug-20 11:55", "status": "resolved", "created": "2015-Aug-13 10:35", "fixed_version": "2015-Aug-13 10:35", "broken_version": "v070600", "priority": "2", "subsystem": "ClassAd", "assigned_to": "johnkn", "derived_from": "#3082", "creator": "jfrey", "rust": "", "customer_group": "chtc", "visibility": "public", "notify": "", "due_date": ""}